53/http://play.raaga.com/telugu/album/Veedinthe-songs-A0002842 | archivedate=1 February 2015 | url-status=live}}</ref>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | ''[[David (2013 Tamil film)|David]]''\n| 2013\n| Tamil\n| \"Maria Pitache\"\n| {{sortname|Remo|Fernandes}}\n| {{sortname|Remo|Fernandes|nolink=1}}\n| style=\"text-align: center;\" |<ref>{{cite news | url=http://ibnlive.in.com/news/david--tamil-music-review-the-soundtrack--boasts-of-trendsetting-music/315811-71-178.html | title=Music Review: David&nbsp;\u2014 The soundtrack boasts of trendsetting music | publisher=CNN-News18 | date=15 January 2013 | agency=IANS | accessdate=1 February 2015 | archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6W2tlOlE8?url=http://ibnlive.in.com/news/david--tamil-music-review-the-soundtrack--boasts-of-trendsetting-music/315811-71-178.html | archivedate=2 February 2015 | url-status=live | df=dmy-all }}</ref>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | ''[[Sketch (2018 film)|Sketch]]''\n| 2018\n| Tamil\n| \"Kanave Kanave\"\n| {{sortname|S. |Thaman}}\n| {{sortname|S.|Thaman|nolink=1}}\n| style=\"text-align: center;\" |<ref>{{cite web |url=https://itunes.apple.com/in/album/sketch-original-motion-picture-soundtrack-ep/1334069589 |title=Sketch (Original Motion Picture Soundtrack) - EP by Thaman S. on Apple Music |date=11 January 2018 |website=[[Apple Music]] |access-date=30 January 2018}}</ref>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | ''[[Saamy Square]]''\n| 2018\n| Tamil\n| \"Pudhu Metro Rail\"\n| Devi Sri Prasad\n| [[Keerthy Suresh]]\n| style=\"text-align: center;\" |<ref>{{cite web|url=https://itunes.apple.com/us/album/saamy-square-original-motion-picture-soundtrack-ep/1415789917|title=Saamy Square (Original Motion Picture Soundtrack) - EP by Devi Sri Prasad on Apple Music|date=24 July 2018|website=[[Apple Music]]|accessdate=19 September 2018}}</ref>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | ''[[Kadaram Kondan]]''\n| 2019\n| Tamil\n| \"Theesudar Kuniyuma\"\n| [[Ghibran]]\n| {{N/A}}\n| style=\"text-align: center;\" |<ref>{{cite web|url=https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/entertainment/tamil/music/kadaraam-kondan-makers-release-new-video-song-titled-theesudar-kuniyuma-from-the-chiyan-vikram-starrer/articleshow/70361991.cms|title='Kadaraam Kondan\u2019: Makers release new video song titled, \u2018'Theesudar Kuniyuma' from the Chiyan Vikram starrer|date=24 July 2019|website=[[Times of India]]|accessdate=3 August 2019}}</ref>\n|}\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist|30em}}\n\n==External links==\n{{Commons category|Vikram}}\n* {{official website|https://web.archive.org/web/20080513222141/http://www.chiyaanvikram.net:80/}}\n* {{IMDb name|id=1417314|name=Vikram}}\n\n{{NationalFilmAwardBestActor}}\n{{FilmfareTamilBestActor}}\n{{TamilNaduStateAwardForBestActor}}\n{{SIIMA Award for Best Actor}}\n{{Authority control}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Vikram}}\n[[Category:Tamil male actors]]\n[[Category:Best Actor National Film Award winners]]\n[[Category:Male actors in Tamil cinema]]\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:Tamil playback singers]]\n[[Category:Loyola College, Chennai alumni]]\n[[Category:Male actors in Hindi cinema]]\n[[Category:Male actors from Chennai]]\n[[Category:1966 births]]\n[[Category:Telugu male actors]]\n[[Category:Male actors in Telugu cinema]]\n[[Category:Indian male film actors]]\n[[Category:Male actors in Malayalam cinema]]\n[[Category:Tamil Nadu State Film Awards winners]]\n[[Category:Filmfare Awards South winners]]\n[[Category:Indian male voice actors]]\n[[Category:Recipients of the Kalaimamani Award]]\n[[Category:20th-century Indian male actors]]\n[[Category:21st-century Indian male actors]]\n[[Category:SIIMA Awards winners]]\n", "name_user": "Subhmanish", "label": "safe", "comment": "fixed template", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Vikram_(actor)"}
